    <subfield code="a">About improving efficiency of the <math altimg="si8.gif" display="inline" id="mml8" overflow="scroll"><msup><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mi>M</mi></math> algorithms when computing the inter-particle forces in beam dynamics</subfield>
  </datafield>
